Package soot.jimple.infoflow.data.pathBuilders

Interface IAbstractionPathBuilder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IMemoryBoundedSolver
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractAbstractionPathBuilder, BatchPathBuilder, ConcurrentAbstractionPathBuilder, ContextInsensitivePathBuilder, ContextInsensitiveSourceFinder, ContextSensitivePathBuilder, EmptyPathBuilder, RecursivePathBuilder
    public interface IAbstractionPathBuilder
extends IMemoryBoundedSolver
    Common interface for all path construction algorithms. These algorithms reconstruct the path from the sink to the source.

    Steven Arzt

        void runIncrementalPathCompuation()
